# Source/original Meshy renders + garment source photos (~178MB of 12–60MB GLBs).
# Only the Draco-compressed copies in static/models/ are used at runtime; shipping
# these originals balloons `railway up` to ~200MB and times the upload out.
/Garment photos for Meshy/
